# 🔄 Main Business Flow

## Scenario: Resident Requests a Plumbing Service
1. Resident opens the app
2. Resident browses available services
3. Resident selects plumbing service
4. Resident chooses location
5. Resident sends request
6. Backend saves the order
7. System matches a nearby service provider
8. Notification is sent to provider
9. Provider accepts the request
10. Resident completes payment
11. Provider performs the service
12. Resident rates and reviews the provider

